@startuml

State "NotLoggedIn"
State "LoggedIn"
State "InvalidLocation"
State "ValidLocation"
State "SelectWeatherInfo"
State "AdditionalDetails"
State "LoggedOut"

[*] NotLoggedIn --> LoggedIn: Register
NotLoggedIn --> InvalidLocation: Login_Failed

LoggedIn --> ValidLocation: Validate_Location
LoggedIn --> InvalidLocation: Login_Failed
ValidLocation --> SelectWeatherInfo: Check_Weather
InvalidLocation --> LoggedOut: Login_Failed
SelectWeatherInfo --> AdditionalDetails: Show_Additional_Details

@enduml
